snippet.title: 1000xRESIST - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
1000xRESIST is a thrilling sci-fi adventure. The year is unknown, and a disease spread by an alien invasion keeps you underground. You are a Watcher. You dutifully fulfill your purpose in serving the ALLMOTHER, until the day you discover a shocking secret that changes everything.
1000xRESIST is now available to wishlist on Steam!
